(157, 'event_test_e', '2012-09-11', '2012-09-30', 'Culture', 0, 0, 'Sjeverni Region', 'Bar', 'bar ground', 'nypyz3wxjl.jpg', 'media/images/nypyz3wxjl.jpg', 'ndxf0fmvtb.flv', 'media/videos/ndxf0fmvtb.flv', '', 0, '<p>test_e</p>', 'eventteste'),
(158, 'Hot winter in the hills', '2014-02-01', '2014-04-30', 'Sports', 0, 0, 'Sjeverni Region', 'Zabljak', 'Kolašin, Šavnik, Nikši?, Rožaje, Cetinje', 'u9uehc3alo.jpg', 'media/images/u9uehc3alo.jpg', '', '', '', 0, '<p>Very rich tourist event with a lot of cultural and artistic events and entertainment. Hot winter in the hills and the numerous programs that are part of it are held in cities sjveru Montenegro, but also on the ski trails and paths of Durmitor, Bjelasica Sinjajevine ... Numerous guest music stars, sports events, various programs, such as in hotels, and in the open, are only part of the rich offerings of this event.</p>', 'hotwinterinthehills'),
(159, 'Days of Camellia', '2013-03-25', '2013-03-28', 'Tourism', 0, 0, 'Primorski region', 'Kotor', 'Stoliv, Kotor', '9qcu0rzh69.jpg', 'media/images/9qcu0rzh69.jpg', '', '', '', 0, '<p>Local event with a rich program dominated camellias and arrangements of it. Over several days, held izloÅ¾bebe arrangements, Bal camellias and camellia choice for the lady, and a series of concerts. According to legend, back in the 1870th The flower is the captain Stoliv brought from the Far East (Japan) to make it a gift to his wife.</p>', 'daysofcamellia'),
(160, 'Golden Snowflake', '2013-03-08', '2013-03-09', 'Concerts', 0, 0, 'Sjeverni Region', 'Savnik', 'Rozaje', 'tpbzyaed7o.png', 'media/images/tpbzyaed7o.png', '', '', '', 0, '<p>Music Festival for Children, which brings together the best young performers and musical artists for children.</p>', 'goldensnowflake');
