(2452, 7, 258, 'short_description', '<p><span style="color: #2a548b; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: left;">Located in one of the oldest settlements on the Adriatic Riviera, Tivat,Vila Iva is 80 metres from a marvellous private sandy beach offering up-to-date, attractive accommodation. The rooms are equipped with international cable TV, in-room safes and wireless internet access. Two deck chairs and a parasol, which can be used on the private beach, are included in the room rate. Many rooms also feature balconies, some of them boast superb views of the Adriatic. The outdoor swimming pool has a sun deck as well as a bar which serves drinks and snacks. The private beach is also fully serviced, featuring a bar. Hotel Tara has an aperitif bar which is open daily as well as a restaurant where delicious buffet breakfasts and dinners are served. Guests can experience the amazing cultural heritage, interesting architecture and a vibrant night life in Budva. The various sandy beaches, coves and small islands around the town are popular with swimmers, sunbathers and boaters..</span></p>', '<p>Nalazi se u jednoj od najstarijih naselja na Jadranu rivijere, Tivat, Vila Iva je 80 metara od predivnoj privatnoj pje&scaron;&#269;anoj pla?i nudi up-to-datum, atraktivan smje&scaron;taj. Sobe su opremljene s me&#273;unarodnim kabel TV, in-room sefovi i be?i&#269;ni pristup internetu. Dvije le?aljke i suncobrane, koji se mogu koristiti na privatnoj pla?i, uklju&#269;eni su u cijenu sobe. Mnogi su sobe tako&#273;er imaju balkone, neki od njih imaju divan pogled na Jadranu.Vanjski bazen ima sun&#269;anu palubu, kao i bar koji slu?i pi&#263;a i zalogaje.Privatna pla?a je tako&#273;er u potpunosti servisirati, s bar. Hotel Tara ima aperitiv bar koji je otvoren svaki dan, kao i restoran u kojem ukusna buffet doru&#269;ak i ve&#269;era se poslu?uju. Gosti mogu iskusiti nevjerojatnu kulturnu ba&scaron;tinu, zanimljive arhitekture i rezonantan no&#263;ni ?ivot u Budvi. Razli&#269;ite pje&scaron;&#269;ane pla?e, uvale i mali otoci oko grada su popularni s kupa&#269;e, nauti&#269;are i sunbathers ...</p>', 'property_type'),
