(2459, 5, 218, 'short_description', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">At a private beach in Herceg Novi overlooking Boka Kotor Bay, Hotel Perla provides free Wi-Fi. It offers elegantly furnished rooms and apartments with balconies and sea views.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Within a short walk on the 4 mile long Setaliste 5 Danica Promenade you can reach the center of Herceg Novi. The nearby Baroque-style Savina Monastery is an interesting historic site.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">The Perla''s restaurant serves local and international cuisine accompanied by aperitifs and a wide selection of wines. Dinner is buffet-style. The cafe bar offers coffee, pastries as well as pizzas and pastas.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Perla Hotel features a gym with a massage room. Anti-cellulite treatments and yoga sessions are offered.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">A lounger and sun shades are provided free of charge for hotel guests. Scuba diving, sailing, water skiing, rides on a speed boat, kayaking and many other activities are offered close to the Perla.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">New rental cars and airport shuttle services are offered at discounted rates for hotel guests.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">', 'property_type'),
