(2468, 7, 213, 'short_description', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Located on a fiord and directly facing a beach on the Adriatic Sea, Villa Iva offers self-catering apartments in Dobrota. The UNESCO-listed old town of Kotor is 4 km away.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Fitted with modern furnishings, air-conditioned apartments at Villa Iva hotel all include a kitchen with cooking utensils and dining area. There is a spacious living room with TV and en-suite bathrooms with hairdryer.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Some apartments open out onto a patio or balconies with views of the surroundings.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Guests will benefit from the convenient location to access grocery shops, restaurants and the local bus station, all within 500 metres from the property. Tivat International Airport is 10 km away.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Smje&scaron;ten na fjorda i neposredno pred pla?a na Jadranu, Villa Iva nudi self-catering apartmana u Dobroti.Na popisu UNESCO-a Stari grad Kotor je 4 km.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Opremljeni s modernim namje&scaron;tajem, klimatizirani apartmani u Villi Iva hotelu uklju&#269;uju sve kuhinju sa posu&#273;e i blagovaonom. Tu je i prostrani dnevni boravak sa TV i en-suite kupaonica sa su&scaron;ilom za kosu.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Neki apartmani otvoriti van na vrt ili terase s pogledom na okolicu.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Gosti &#263;e imati koristi od prikladnog mjesta za pristup prodavaonica prehrambenih namirnica, trgovine, restorani i lokalne autobusne stanice, sve u roku od 500 metara od imovine. Tivat International Airport je 10 km.</div>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>Smje&scaron;ten na fjorda i neposredno pred pla?a na Jadranu, Villa Iva nudi self-catering apartmana u Dobroti.Na popisu UNESCO-a Stari grad Kotor je 4 km.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Opremljeni s modernim namje&scaron;tajem, klimatizirani apartmani u Villi Iva hotelu uklju&#269;uju sve kuhinju sa posu&#273;e i blagovaonom. Tu je i prostrani dnevni boravak sa TV i en-suite kupaonica sa su&scaron;ilom za kosu.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Neki apartmani otvoriti van na vrt ili terase s pogledom na okolicu.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Gosti &#263;e imati koristi od prikladnog mjesta za pristup prodavaonica prehrambenih namirnica, trgovine, restorani i lokalne autobusne stanice, sve u roku od 500 metara od imovine. Tivat International Airport je 10 km.</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'property_type'),
