(2471, 5, 204, 'short_description', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Surrounded by an olive grove and cypress trees, Hotel Pharos offers air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi. Its private beach is 600 metres away and there is a beach shuttle bus.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Every room is equipped with a refrigerator and satellite TV. The bathrooms have a shower and hairdryer. Most rooms have a private balcony.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Guests can relax in the garden, under the shade of the lemon and orange trees. There is a shared rooftop terrace, and the restaurant serves national dishes.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">At the hotel&rsquo;s private beach, guests can find sun loungers and a bar selling drinks and ice creams. Paddle boats are also available for rent at the beach, while cars and bikes can be rented directly at the hotel. Guests can use the hotel''s bus to the beach, which leaves on demand and is available against a small fee.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">The Pharos is 1.5 km away from the railway station and 1.2 km from the bus station. Tivat and Podgorica airports are about 48 km away. Excursions to the old town can be arranged.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Окруженный оливковыми деревь', 'property_type'),
