(2475, 5, 189, 'short_description', '<p>Set at the foot of Sinjajevina Mountain, Hotel &amp; Resort Gacka offers a wellness centre with an indoor pool. Activities include rafting in River Tara, paragliding and horseback riding.  All rooms here are set in beautiful wooden cottages. Each room has its own private entrance, and they all come with a satellite TV and a minibar.  At the spa, natural light floods the indoor pool room, with its large windows looking out to the surrounding mountains. There is also a jacuzzi, several saunas, and a fitness studio. Tennis and basketball courts are also available.  Gacka Hotel is 4 km away from Mojkovac&rsquo;s town centre. The entrance to Biogradsko Lake Natural Park is less than 10 km away.</p>', '<p>У', 'property_type'),
