(2523, 5, 211, 'short_description', '<p>Quietly situated in Bar, 3 km from the beach, Montenegro House offers air-conditioned apartments with satellite TV and balconies. A scheduled shuttle service to the beach is included.  The kitchen features a fridge, microwave and tea/coffee maker. There are 2 bathrooms available.  The Montenegro House offers free access to the outdoor swimming pool and barbecue facilities are provided.  There is a grocery store within easy walking distance. Upon request, a transport from and to the airports of Podgorica and Tivat or the beaches of Petrovac and Ulcinj is available.</p>', '<p>Ра', 'property_type'),
(2524, 7, 211, 'short_description', '<p>Quietly situated in Bar, 3 km from the beach, Montenegro House offers air-conditioned apartments with satellite TV and balconies. A scheduled shuttle service to the beach is included.  The kitchen features a fridge, microwave and tea/coffee maker. There are 2 bathrooms available.  The Montenegro House offers free access to the outdoor swimming pool and barbecue facilities are provided.  There is a grocery store within easy walking distance. Upon request, a transport from and to the airports of Podgorica and Tivat or the beaches of Petrovac and Ulcinj is available.</p>', '<p>Tiho nalazi u Baru, 3 km od pla?e, Crna Gora Kuća nudi klimatizirane apartmane sa satelitskom TV i balkonima.Rasporedu shuttle servis do pla?e je uklju', 'property_type'),
