(2528, 7, 210, 'short_description', '<p>Seat in the peaceful village of Susanj and only 1.5 km from the beach, Vila Zada is surrounded by a garden. It offers air-conditioned rooms and free Wi-Fi. Free on-site private parking is provided.  The en-suite rooms at Zada are simply furnished and feature tiled floors. They offer satellite TV, a safe and a seating area with a sofa. Most rooms include a balcony.  A 24-hour front desk service is guaranteed in the Vila. Guests can make use of free bikes that available on site to explore the surrounding sites.  The centre of Bar with numerous dining and shopping options is 2.5 km away. Podgorica Airport is 45 km away, and Tivat Airport is 60 km away.</p>', '<p>Smjestena u mirnom selu Susanj, a samo 1,5 km od pla?e, Vila Zada je okru?ena vrtom. Ona nudi klimatizirane sobe i besplatni Wi-Fi. Besplatno na licu mjesta, privatni parking je pru?ena. The en-suite sobe u Zada jednostavno su namje&scaron;teni i imaju poplo', 'property_type'),
