#269;ki kolodvor i glavna autobusna stanica su 1 km od imovine. Parking je besplatan na Baki&#263; gost ku&#263;i.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'property_type'),
(2543, 7, 212, 'short_description', '<p>Enjoying a superb location close to the stunning Plavi Horizonti Beach on the Montenegrin coast in Tivat, the self-catering Maki Apartments boast a peaceful spot in the Radovici area.  Whether you enjoy diving, volleyball or simply lying back and soaking up the sun, this Blue Flag beach provides the highest hospitality standards.  Your dedicated hosts will be happy to assist with your requests, and car rental, free parking and laundry facilities are just some of the elements that will make your holiday a pleasant one.  Shuttle service is also available to and from Tivat International Airport (TIV) and other transfers can also be arranged through the Maki Apartments.  The apartments are clean, fresh and classically decorated to create an ambiance of space and liberty. Furnished with a mini-kitchen, en suite bathroom and private terrace, guests will find plenty of room for independent living. Each apartment has a modem stick for free access to the internet.  You can also rent a car and explore the Montenegrin coast and environment. This service needs to be scheduled before arrival.</p>', '', 'property_type'),
(2544, 5, 210, 'short_description', '<p>Seat in the peaceful village of Susanj and only 1.5 km from the beach, Vila Zada is surrounded by a garden. It offers air-conditioned rooms and free Wi-Fi. Free on-site private parking is provided.  The en-suite rooms at Zada are simply furnished and feature tiled floors. They offer satellite TV, a safe and a seating area with a sofa. Most rooms include a balcony.  A 24-hour front desk service is guaranteed in the Vila. Guests can make use of free bikes that available on site to explore the surrounding sites.  The centre of Bar with numerous dining and shopping options is 2.5 km away. Podgorica Airport is 45 km away, and Tivat Airport is 60 km away.</p>', '', 'property_type'),
