(2583, 5, 182, 'short_description', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Set in the heart of Tivat in the Bay of Kotor, Villa Nena Appartments is located only 20 metres away from the Adriatic Sea. It offers air-conditioned apartments with a balcony or a patio and free Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p>All of the apartments at Villa Nena feature a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. A fully equipped kitchenette and a bathroom with a washing machine are also available. Some apartments offer a sea view.</p>\r\n<p>A large garden surrounds the house and includes a barbecue terrace. Against an extra charge, the hotel also provides a pick-up service from the Tivat Airport, which is 5 km away.</p>\r\n<p>Dining and shopping options, as well as nightlife, are all plentiful on the Tivat&rsquo;s sea-side promenade, which is just steps away. The town centre can be reached within 1.5 km. Porto Montenegro Marina is only 50 metres away.</p>\r\n<p>Tivat Bus Station is 1.5 km away. Free parking at a nearby location is provided at Villa Nena.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">&#1054;&#1090;&#1077;&#1083;&#1100; &#1088;&#1072;&#1089;&#1087;&#1086;&#1083;&#1072;&#1075;&#1072;&#1077;&#1090;&#1089;&#1103; &#1074; &#1094;&#1077;&#1085;&#1090;&#1088;&#1077; &#1075;&#1086;&#1088;&#1086;&#1076;&#1072; &#1058;&#1080;&#1074;&#1072;&#1090; &#1074; &#1050;&#1086;&#1090;&#1086;&#1088;&#1089;&#1082;&#1086;&#1081; &#1073;&#1091;&#1093;&#1090;&#1077;, &#1042;&#1080;&#1083;&#1083;&#1072; &#1053;&#1077;&#1085;&#1072; &#1082;&#1074;&#1072;&#1088;&#1090;&#1080;&#1088; &#1088;&#1072;&#1089;&#1087;&#1086;&#1083;&#1086;&#1078;&#1077;&#1085; &#1074;&#1089;&#1077;&#1075;&#1086; &#1074; 20 &#1084;&#1077;&#1090;&#1088;&#1072;&#1093; &#1086;&#1090; &#1040;&#1076;&#1088;&#1080;&#1072;&#1090;&#1080;&#1095;&#1077;&#1089;&#1082;&#1086;&#1075;&#1086; &#1084;&#1086;&#1088;&#1103;. &#1054;&#1085; &#1087;&#1088;&#1077;&#1076;&