(2849, 5, 291, 'short_description', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">Located on Trebjesa Mountain, just above the city of Nik&scaron;i?, Hotel Trebjesa is surrounded by mountains and pine forests. The on-site restaurant features traditional and international specialties.</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">All rooms feature air-conditioning and offer cable TV, a minibar and a safe. Private bathroom features free toiletries and a hairdryer.</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">The hotel features unique architecture and a covered lookout spot that offers views of the entire city. The front desk is open 24 hours a day, while laundry and ironing service can be arranged upon request.</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">Free Wi-Fi is featured in the entire hotel, while guests can enjoy free parking and bicycle rental. Breakfast is served each day at the hotel restaurant. The hotel restaurant features a spacious terrace and a bar.The centre of Nik&scaron;i? can be reached in a 20-minute walk. Lakes Slano and Krupac can be reached in 5 km, while Vu?je Ski Centre is 20 km away. Podgorica Airport is located 70 km from Hotel Trebjesa.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<div id="gt-res-content" class="almost_half_cell">\r\n<div style="zoom: 1;" dir="ltr"><span id="result_box" lang="ru"><span class="hps">&ETH;&nbsp;&ETH;&deg;&Ntilde;', 'property_type'),
(2850, 7, 291, 'short_description', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">Located on Trebjesa Mountain, just above the city of Nik&scaron;i?, Hotel Trebjesa is surrounded by mountains and pine forests. The on-site restaurant features traditional and international specialties.</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">All rooms feature air-conditioning and offer cable TV, a minibar and a safe. Private bathroom features free toiletries and a hairdryer.</span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">The hotel features unique architecture and a covered lookout spot that offers views of the entire city. The front desk is open 24 hours a day, while laundry and ironing service can be arranged upon request.</span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">Free Wi-Fi is featured in the entire hotel, while guests can enjoy free parking and bicycle rental. Breakfast is served each day at the hotel restaurant. The hotel restaurant features a spacious terrace and a bar.The centre of Nik&scaron;i? can be reached in a 20-minute walk. Lakes Slano and Krupac can be reached in 5 km, while Vu?je Ski Centre is 20 km away. Podgorica Airport is located 70 km from Hotel Trebjesa.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Smje&scaron;ten na Trebjese planine, tik iznad grada Nik&scaron;i?a, Hotel Trebjese je okru?en planinama i borove &scaron;ume.Restoran na licu mjesta ima tradicionalne i me?unarodne specijalitete.<br />Sve sobe imaju klima-ure?aj i TV s kabelskim programima, mini bar i sef. Privatna kupaonica ima besplatne toaletne potrep&scaron;tine i su&scaron;ilo za kosu.<br />Hotel ima jedinstvenu arhitekturu i natkrivenu vidikovcu mjestu koje se pru?a pogled na cijeli grad.Recepcija je otvorena 24 sata dnevno, dok pranja i peglanja mo?e organizirati na zahtjev.</p>\r\n<p>Besplatan Wi-Fi je sadr?anu u cijelom hotelu, a gosti mogu u?ivati ??besplatan parking i bicikala. Doru?ak se poslu?uje svaki dan u hotelskom restoranu.Hotelski restoran ima prostranu terasu i bar.Sredi&scaron;te Nik&scaron;i? mo?e do?i u 20-ak minuta hoda. Jezera Slano i Krupac mo?e do?i u 5 km, dok Vu?je Ski centar je udaljen 20 km. Zra?na luka Podgorica nalazi se 70 km od hotela Trebjese.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'property_type'),
