(3000, 5, 176, 'description', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">It includes the plateau interspersed with many canyons, above which rise the imposing mountain peaks. For the name of Durmitor is considered to be descended from a Celtic word that means "mountain full of water," And that is exactly one of the characteristics of this national park. It beautifies 18 glacial lakes, you called another mountain eyes. The largest and most attractive is the Black Lake, while the highest peak Bobotov hip.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Tara River Canyon, located in the north of the park is particularly impressed by its beauty. As the second largest canyon in the world, but also because of the famous river for rafting, visits it every year a large number of tourists. <br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Durmitor is also popular with nature lovers because it is rich in flora and fauna. Over 1,300 species, many of which are relict, and there are 36 endemic species, of which 6 can be seen only on Durmitor. One of the few untouched forests of black pine is right here. In many forests that adorn this national park live brown bear, wild pigs chamois and wild cats, as well as various bird species. The Tara River is particularly rich in salmon.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">In this region you can find numerous monuments of culture is from the ancient period. Most of those from the Middle Ages such as the ruins of towns and villages, bridges and burial.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', 'Она включает в ', 'content_type'),
