(3877, 7, 344, 'short_description', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">Overlooking the Bay of Kotor and only 330 yards from the beach, Apartments Mediteran is situated in the center of Herceg Novi. It offers air-conditioned apartments with minibar and balcony.All apartments have panoramic views of the sea, private bathrooms and kitchenettes.Tennis courts, restaurants and 24-hour shops are nearby. Herceg Novi&rsquo;s 600-year-old fortress and the 9 miles beach, known as Riviera, are only a short walk from Apartments Mediteran.The Mediteran is within 30 miles of Dubrovnik and there is a local bus station within a 5-minute walk from the property.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Prekrasan pogled na Bokokotorski zaliv i samo 330 metara od plaže, Apartmani Mediteran nalazi se u samom centru Herceg Novog. Nudi klimatizirane apartmane s mini bar i balkon.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Svi apartmani imaju panoramski pogled na more, privatne kupaonice i kuhinje.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Teniski tereni, restorani i 24-satni trgovine su u blizini. 600-godi&scaron;nja tvrđavi Herceg Novog i 9 milja plaže, poznata kao Rivijera, samo nekoliko minuta hoda od apartmana Mediteran.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Mediteran je u roku od 30 milja od Dubrovnika, a postoji i lokalne autobusne stanice u roku od 5 minuta hoda od imovine.</div>\r\n<p>Prekrasan pogled na Bokokotorski zaliv i samo 330 metara od plaže, Apartmani Mediteran nalazi se u samom centru Herceg Novog. Nudi klimatizirane apartmane s mini bar i balkon. Svi apartmani imaju panoramski pogled na more, privatne kupaonice i kuhinje.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Teniski tereni, restorani i 24-satni trgovine su u blizini. 600-godi&scaron;nja tvrđavi Herceg Novog i 9 milja plaže, poznata kao Rivijera, samo nekoliko minuta hoda od apartmana Mediteran.</p>\r\n<p>Mediteran je u roku od 30 milja od Dubrovnika, a postoji i lokalne autobusne stanice u roku od 5 minuta hoda od imovine.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'property_type'),
