(186, '10001-2', 298, 24, 'Hotel Dominus', 7, 'Djordja Stanica 31', 'Bijelo Polje', '84000', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 17, 'wq72763cf3.jpg', '123456789-012345-678', 'hoteldominus', '75', '0', 43.034332, 19.75032, 17, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Set within a 5-minute walk from the centre of Bijelo Polje, this hotel offers free Wi-Fi access and free private parking. The E763 motorway is 200 metres away.  All rooms at the Dominus come with cable TV, a seating area with leather armchairs and a private bathroom with bathtub or shower. The rooms are decorated with warm beige and brown colours.  The 24-hour reception provides a safety deposit box and ironing as well as laundry services.  Guests can start their day with a buffet breakfast and have a drink at the lounge bar.  Hotel Dominus is a 10-minute drive from the Bijelo Polje Train Station. Numerous bars, restaurants and a market are within a 5-10-minute walk away.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(189, '10002-2', 298, 24, 'Hotel & Resort Gacka', 7, 'Gacka bb', 'Mojkovac', '84205', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 4, 10, 'o47epnoaog.jpg', '123456789-012345-678', 'hotelresortgacka', '75', '0', 42.96, 19.58, 10, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Set at the foot of Sinjajevina Mountain, Hotel &amp; Resort Gacka offers a wellness centre with an indoor pool. Activities include rafting in River Tara, paragliding and horseback riding.  All rooms here are set in beautiful wooden cottages. Each room has its own private entrance, and they all come with a satellite TV and a minibar.  At the spa, natural light floods the indoor pool room, with its large windows looking out to the surrounding mountains. There is also a jacuzzi, several saunas, and a fitness studio. Tennis and basketball courts are also available.  Gacka Hotel is 4 km away from Mojkovac&rsquo;s town centre. The entrance to Biogradsko Lake Natural Park is less than 10 km away.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(190, '20003-2', 298, 47, 'Ambiente', 7, 'Mojsija Zecevica bb', 'Berane', '84300', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 0, 'atzu9zl1cd.jpg', '', 'ambiente', '103', '9', 42.845529, 19.873946, 0, '4, 7', '<p>Well decorated restaurant on two levels. Often the promotion of local cuisine, especially the polenta and Priganica.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
