(198, '20005-2', 298, 24, 'Apartmani Konjevic', 9, 'Bokeljskih mornara 25', 'Herceg Novi', '85340', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 4, 3, 'czfes3bkgw.jpg', '123456789-012345-678', 'apartmanikonjevic', '68', '0', 42.450837, 18.551509, 3, '4, 7', '<p>Apartments Konjevic to the settlement Savina, one of the most beautiful parts of Herceg Novi. The building was built and equipped 2009th Whatever. and is located on the coast, close to the 7 km long promenade Pet Danica. If you arrive by car, free parking is available and there are good links with the nearby airports, Tivat (25 km) and Dubrovnik (30 km). All apartments are located on the second floor and a terrace with a view ...</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(199, '10006-2', 298, 24, 'Hotel Tara', 9, 'Becici', 'Budva', '85310', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 4, 227, '37zwt8hfz1.jpg', '123456789-012345-678', 'hoteltara', '75', '0', 42.28258, 18.861766, 227, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Located in one of the oldest settlements on the Adriatic Riviera, Becici Budva, Hotel Tara is 80 metres from a marvellous private sandy beach offering up-to-date, attractive accommodation.  The rooms are equipped with international cable TV, in-room safes and wireless internet access. Two deck chairs and a parasol, which can be used on the private beach, are included in the room rate. Many rooms also feature balconies, some of them boast superb views of the Adriatic.  The outdoor swimming pool has a sun deck as well as a bar which serves drinks and snacks. The private beach is also fully serviced, featuring a bar.  Hotel Tara has an aperitif bar which is open daily as well as a restaurant where delicious buffet breakfasts and dinners are served.  Guests can experience the amazing cultural heritage, interesting architecture and a vibrant night life in Budva. The various sandy beaches, coves and small islands around the town are popular with swimmers, sunbathers and boaters.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1);
