(201, '20007-2', 298, 24, 'Hotel Becici', 9, 'Becici', 'Budva', '85310', '38220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 15, 'g1iqvujage.jpg', '12456', 'hotelbecici', '3', '0', 42.282341, 18.874705, 15, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Becici hotel, situated in an attractive location that occupies a central place on the Becici beach, 4 km away from Budva. Surrounded by greenery, the hotel is ideal for family holidays.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(203, '3-2', 298, 47, 'Montevideo Pub', 8, 'Stanka Dragojevica 42', 'Podgorica', '81000', '+38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 0, 'w1q4fjqr9q.jpg', '12456', 'montevideopub', '79', '0', 42.441731, 19.259919, 0, '', '<p>In Montevideo pub you Expected home And atmosphere. Frequent gigs and always interesting company!&nbsp;</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(204, '10001-2', 298, 24, 'Hotel Pharos', 9, 'Bjelisi 13', 'Bar', '85000', '38220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', 'www.hotelpharos.me', 5, 15, 'qnsrenqsv9.jpg', '12456', 'hotelpharos', '75', '0', 42.055462, 19.122477, 15, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Surrounded by an olive grove and cypress trees, Hotel Pharos offers air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi. Its private beach is 600 metres away and there is a beach shuttle bus.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Every room is equipped with a refrigerator and satellite TV. The bathrooms have a shower and hairdryer. Most rooms have a private balcony.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Guests can relax in the garden, under the shade of the lemon and orange trees. There is a shared rooftop terrace, and the restaurant serves national dishes.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">At the hotel&rsquo;s private beach, guests can find sun loungers and a bar selling drinks and ice creams. Paddle boats are also available for rent at the beach, while cars and bikes can be rented directly at the hotel. Guests can use the hotel''s bus to the beach, which leaves on demand and is available against a small fee.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">The Pharos is 1.5 km away from the railway station and 1.2 km from the bus station. Tivat and Podgorica airports are about 48 km away. Excursions to the old town can be arranged.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(205, '20001-2', 339, 24, 'Villa Bjelasica', 7, 'Biocinovici bb', 'Kolasin', '81210', '38267460122', '667160', 'vila.bjelasica@gmail.com', '', 4, 5, '4o43jg4mf0.jpg', '', 'villabjelasica', '3', '0', 42.821721, 19.51792, 5, '4', '<p>Surrounded by mountains of Bjelasica, Sinjajevina and Komovi, Villa Bjelasica is set 3 km from the centre of Kola&scaron;in. Featuring a gym and a sauna, it offers free Wi-Fi, free parking and accommodation with balconies.  All accommodation units have an LCD cable TV and a DVD player. They comprise hardwood floors and wooden and stone wall elements. Each unit provides a private bathroom.  A garden with a terrace is at guests&rsquo; disposal. A pool table is also available. Savardak, a wooden cone shaped restaurant, serving traditional Montenegrin cuisine is 100 metres away.  Biogradska Gora National Park with its Biogradsko Lake, one of the three last jungles in Europe, is within a 16-km reach. The 13th century Moraca Monastery is at a distance of 25 km.  Kola&scaron;in Train Station is 3 km away. Podgorica International Airport is 70 km from the Bjelasica.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(206, '20002-2', 339, 24, 'Apartments Rajsko Selo', 7, 'Put ka skijalistu', 'Kolasin', '81210', '67520850', '667160', 'hotelkerber@t-com.me', '', 3, 5, 'uwks7lr2y5.jpg', '', 'apartmentsrajskoselo', '68', '0', 42.822603, 19.514465, 5, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Apartment Rajsko Selo offers unique and colourful bungalows built in old mountain style and set in the untouched Montenegrin nature. Barbecue facilities on the river banks are free for use for all guests.  Apartments are decorated in natural colours and equipped with a seating area and satellite TV. A fully equipped kitchen is available, while the private bathroom provides a shower. The patio overlooks the mountains and the river.  The nearest restaurant can be reached in just 10 metres and a market is available 500 metres from the Rajsko Selo. The centre of Kolasin is 2 km away. Guests are also welcome to visit Biogradska Gora National Park, 17 km away.  A ski centre, Jezerine Bjelasica, is available 5 km away, while a tennis court is located just 1 km from the property. Guests can enjoy rafting on the river or snow sports during the winter.  Bus and Train Stations in Kolasin are 2 km from the property, while the Podgorica Airport is 75 km away.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(207, '20003-2', 339, 24, 'Guest Accommodation Bakic', 7, 'Brace Vujisic bb', 'Kolasin', '81210', '069414900', '667160', 'gab@gmail.com', '', 3, 4, 'glw5mqfdfv.jpg', '', 'guestaccommodationbakic', '68', '0', 42.820987, 19.523111, 4, '4, 7', '<p>The peaceful Guest Accommodation Bakic is 10 km from the Kola&scaron;in ski resort, and is surrounded by a garden and an orchard. The town centre is 300 metres away, and free Wi-Fi access is available.  All units have their own bathroom, TV and central heating. The studio has its own kitchen and a private entrance. Guests staying in the room without cooking facilities can use the shared kitchen or the original brick barbecue in the garden.  National Park Biogradska Gora is 15 km, Podgorica Airport is 80 km away. The next railway station and the main bus stop are 1 km from the property. Parking is free of charge at the Bakic guest house.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(208, '20004-2', 339, 24, 'Apartments Bojanic', 9, 'Ilino 23', 'Bar', '85000', '069414900', '667160', 'ab@gmail.com', '', 2, 6, '9gc87wybtq.jpg', '', 'apartmentsbojanic', '3', '0', 42.110632, 19.088616, 6, '4, 7', '<p>Just a 5-minute walk away from the 2 km-long beach, Apartments Bojanic are located in Bar-Susanj. All apartments are air-conditioned and have a fully equipped kitchenette and private bathroom with toiletries.  You can make free use of the large rooftop terrace. There you can find barbecue facilities, tables and chair. Free Wi-Fi is available in the entire building.  Free transfers from the bus and train stations as well as from the port are offered. Free private parking is possible on site.  The centre of Bar and the ferry port are 1.5 km away from the Bojanic apartments. The nearest restaurant and the nearest caf&eacute; bar are just a 3-minute walk away.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(209, '20002-2', 298, 24, 'Apartments Vesna', 9, 'Lepetane bb', 'Tivat', '85320', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 7, '1x8b1wmhl9.jpg', '', 'apartmentsvesna', '68', '0', 42.46662, 18.686993, 7, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Apartments VESNA is located next to a pebbled beach. It offers air-conditioned apartments with free Wi-Fi. A garden with barbecue facilities and a large table are suited for enjoying a meal outdoors.  All apartments are fully furnished and equipped with a seating area and satellite TV. A fully equipped kitchenette is available. Private bathroom provides a shower and free toiletries.  The nearest grocery store is 300 metres from the apartment, and there is a large supermarket 3 km away. A restaurant is situated 1.5 km from the house. Tennis courts can be found 2.5 km from the Vesna.  The centre of Tivat can be reached in 5 km. Porto Montenegro Marina, featuring casinos, a promenade and several restaurants, is 3.5 km away.  Guests have access to free parking in front of the house. Airport Tivat is 7km from the house, while Dubrovnik Airport in Croatia can be reached in 40 km.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(210, '20005-2', 339, 24, 'Vila Zada', 9, 'Ilino bb', 'Bar', '85000', '069414900', '667160', 'perovic@blic.net', '', 2, 11, 'nfz27nzlfb.jpg', '', 'vilazada', '3', '0', 42.105773, 19.091006, 11, '4', '<p>Seat in the peaceful village of Susanj and only 1.5 km from the beach, Vila Zada is surrounded by a garden. It offers air-conditioned rooms and free Wi-Fi. Free on-site private parking is provided.  The en-suite rooms at Zada are simply furnished and feature tiled floors. They offer satellite TV, a safe and a seating area with a sofa. Most rooms include a balcony.  A 24-hour front desk service is guaranteed in the Vila. Guests can make use of free bikes that available on site to explore the surrounding sites.  The centre of Bar with numerous dining and shopping options is 2.5 km away. Podgorica Airport is 45 km away, and Tivat Airport is 60 km away.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(211, '20006-2', 339, 24, 'Montenegro House', 9, 'Polje', 'Bar', '85000', '069414900', '667160', 'mh@gmail.com', '', 0, 6, '1i9eybzc1e.jpg', '', 'montenegrohouse', '3', '0', 42.09231, 19.118143, 6, '5, 7', '<p>Quietly situated in Bar, 3 km from the beach, Montenegro House offers air-conditioned apartments with satellite TV and balconies. A scheduled shuttle service to the beach is included.  The kitchen features a fridge, microwave and tea/coffee maker. There are 2 bathrooms available.  The Montenegro House offers free access to the outdoor swimming pool and barbecue facilities are provided.  There is a grocery store within easy walking distance. Upon request, a transport from and to the airports of Podgorica and Tivat or the beaches of Petrovac and Ulcinj is available.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(212, '20003-2', 298, 24, 'Maki Apartments', 9, 'Radovici bb', 'Tivat', '85320', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 13, '5cbolgdlho.jpg', '', 'makiapartments', '68', '0', 42.390977, 18.673689, 13, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Enjoying a superb location close to the stunning Plavi Horizonti Beach on the Montenegrin coast in Tivat, the self-catering Maki Apartments boast a peaceful spot in the Radovici area.  Whether you enjoy diving, volleyball or simply lying back and soaking up the sun, this Blue Flag beach provides the highest hospitality standards.  Your dedicated hosts will be happy to assist with your requests, and car rental, free parking and laundry facilities are just some of the elements that will make your holiday a pleasant one.  Shuttle service is also available to and from Tivat International Airport (TIV) and other transfers can also be arranged through the Maki Apartments.  The apartments are clean, fresh and classically decorated to create an ambiance of space and liberty. Furnished with a mini-kitchen, en suite bathroom and private terrace, guests will find plenty of room for independent living. Each apartment has a modem stick for free access to the internet.  You can also rent a car and explore the Montenegrin coast and environment. This service needs to be scheduled before arrival.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(213, '10001-2', 314, 24, 'Vila Iva', 9, 'Kriva ulica bb', 'Kotor', '85340', '38267220971', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 3, 'n3i3cz1lds.jpg', '123456789-012345-678', 'vilaiva', '68', '0', 42.451431, 18.765314, 3, '4, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Located on a fiord and directly facing a beach on the Adriatic Sea, Villa Iva offers self-catering apartments in Dobrota. The UNESCO-listed old town of Kotor is 4 km away.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Fitted with modern furnishings, air-conditioned apartments at Villa Iva hotel all include a kitchen with cooking utensils and dining area. There is a spacious living room with TV and en-suite bathrooms with hairdryer.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Some apartments open out onto a patio or balconies with views of the surroundings.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Guests will benefit from the convenient location to access grocery shops, restaurants and the local bus station, all within 500 metres from the property. Tivat International Airport is 10 km away.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
