(217, '10007-2', 298, 24, 'Vila Panonija', 9, 'Put bokeljske brigade', 'Kotor', '33340', '38220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 7, '39uqhpdgec.jpg', '', 'vilapanonija', '68', '0', 42.430774, 18.76776, 7, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Just 165 ft from Kotor Bay and a 5-minute walk from the beach, Vila Panonija features air conditioned suites and apartments with a private balcony and free Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">The suites and apartments at The Panonija are modern in style and feature parquet floors. They have a private bathroom with a bathtub or shower.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Guests can enjoy their breakfast in the breakfast room, which has stained glass decorations and an adjoining bar area. Open-air caf&eacute;s, pizzerias, and eateries are just a 5-minute walk from Vila Panonija.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">The San Giovanni mountains provide a unique natural backdrop to Kotor and the bay from Panonija''s grounds. With free parking, Tivat Airport is 25 miles away.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(218, '10001-2', 343, 24, 'Hotel Perla', 9, 'Setaliste pet danica', 'Herceg Novi', '85340', '38220620478', '667160', 'milan.perovic@sunnymontenegro.com', '', 4, 41, '5tj31pe5tq.jpg', '123456789-012345-678', 'hotelperla', '75', '0', 42.45041, 18.541124, 41, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">At a private beach in Herceg Novi overlooking Boka Kotor Bay, Hotel Perla provides free Wi-Fi. It offers elegantly furnished rooms and apartments with balconies and sea views.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Within a short walk on the 4 mile long Setaliste 5 Danica Promenade you can reach the center of Herceg Novi. The nearby Baroque-style Savina Monastery is an interesting historic site.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">The Perla''s restaurant serves local and international cuisine accompanied by aperitifs and a wide selection of wines. Dinner is buffet-style. The cafe bar offers coffee, pastries as well as pizzas and pastas.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">Perla Hotel features a gym with a massage room. Anti-cellulite treatments and yoga sessions are offered.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">A lounger and sun shades are provided free of charge for hotel guests. Scuba diving, sailing, water skiing, rides on a speed boat, kayaking and many other activities are offered close to the Perla.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 16px; text-align: left; font-size: small;">New rental cars and airport shuttle services are offered at discounted rates for hotel guests.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(219, '20002-2', 306, 24, 'Volonterski kamp', 8, 'Glava Zete', 'Danilovgrad', '81410', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 3, 'cjie98e0m6.jpg', '1234', 'volonterskikamp', '43', '0', 42.601999, 19.069004, 3, '5, 7', '<p>Two parcels (4000 and 8000 square meters) in the very heart of oak and beech wood, on the river bank. Spring water (pipeline). Complete sanitary infrastructure.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(230, '10001-2', 343, 24, 'Captain Apartments', 9, 'Mediteranska', 'Budva', '85310', '+38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 2, 't72bgfmy44.jpg', '', 'captainapartments', '68', '0', 42.279563, 18.836017, 2, '4, 5', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Apartments is located in the center of Budva, 650 ft from the beach. It offers individually furnished apartments with air conditioning and free access to Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p>Accommodations have a balcony which overlooks the surrounding greenery. A kitchen with a refrigerator and a private bathroom are also available.</p>\r\n<p>Guests can relax on the sunny terrace or explore the Old Town of Budva which can be reached within a 5-minute walk. Markets, restaurants and bars can also be found there.</p>\r\n<p>Captain Apartments offers a 24-hour front desk and free private parking on site.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1),
