(303, '10013-3', 298, 24, 'Hotel Grand', 8, 'Njegoševa 45', 'Cetinje', '81250', '020420478', '667160', '', '', 4, 56, '0lnt25ivqk.jpg', '', 'hotelgrand', '75', '0', 42.398187, 18.915582, 56, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Featuring an indoor pool, sauna and bowling, Hotel Grand Cetinje is surrounded by a park. It offers free Wi-Fi and free underground parking. Budva, the nearest beach, is 18 miles away.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">All rooms come with satellite TV, a minibar and balcony. The private bathrooms have bathrobes, slippers and hairdryers.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Guests can dine at one of the 2 restaurants of the Hotel Grand Cetinje. A pastry shop and an aperitif bar are available as well.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">The library offers a quiet place to unwind. Guests can also have fun at the nightclub. The public tennis court is in the park next to the hotel.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">The local bus station is 1300 ft away and Podgorica Airport is 23 miles from the Grand Hotel.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(304, '10014-3', 298, 24, 'Hotel Kula Damjanova', 7, 'Vojno selo', 'Plav', '84325', '020620478', '667160', '', '', 4, 44, 'lrgqbzvb62.jpg', '', 'hotelkuladamjanova', '75', '0', 42.587893, 19.929156, 44, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Set within the peaceful Komnenovo Ethno Village located on the banks of Lake Plav, Hotel Kula Damjanova offers private lake access, a beach and a refined rustic restaurant serving traditional Montenegrin cuisine.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Kula&rsquo;s rooms are carefully decorated in local ethno style with hand-crafted carpets and textiles. They offer wooden floors, stony walls and a flat-screen TV with cable reception.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">The public areas are furnished in a similar authentic local style and feature hand-carved wooden furniture and a bar with a fireplace. Free Wi-Fi is available in Kula&rsquo;s public areas.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Numerous hiking and biking paths are available around the hotel. There is also a football pitch. Lake Plav offers excellent possibilities for fishing.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Guests can reach the centre of Plav within a 1.2 km walk. Grlja Waterfall is 18 km away. Podgorica with its airport is 140 km away. Free on-site parking is provided.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(305, '10002-3', 307, 24, 'Hotel Breza', 7, 'Danka Mitrova 11', 'Berane', '84300', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 9, 'uihv0y89x1.jpg', '', 'hotelbreza', '74', '0', 42.845, 19.874444, 9, '5, 7', '<p>Description</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(306, '10003-3', 331, 24, 'Motel Durmitor', 7, 'Durmitorska bb', 'Pljevlja', '84210', '0038269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 6, 'kd3hv4holz.jpg', '', 'moteldurmitor', '73', '0', 43.359946, 19.355249, 6, '5, 7', '<p>description</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(307, '10015-3', 298, 24, 'Hotel Terminus', 8, 'Mitra  Bakica bb', 'Podgorica', '81000', '0038220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 4, 10, 'zyelfewpxs.jpg', '', 'hotelterminus', '75', '0', 42.431262, 19.267884, 10, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Opened in November 2012 and offering free airport pick-up, Hotel Terminus is located 500 metres from Podgorica&rsquo;s Old City. It offers free video-surveilled parking, restaurant and air-conditioned interiors with free Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p>All rooms and suites comprise a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a desk and a minibar. Each unit has a private bathroom with a shower.</p>\r\n<p>Podgorica Bus and Train Stations are within 50 metres. A shopping centre is only 500 metres away. Podgorica Airport is at a distance of 7 km. Skadarsko Lake National Park is 20 km from the Terminus Hotel.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(308, '20016-3', 298, 47, 'La Bocca', 9, 'Slovenska plaza bb', 'Budva', '85310', '11111111111111111', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', 'http://www.labocca.astoriamontenegro.com/', 3, 2, 'ubz8v3coyh.jpg', '', 'labocca', '103', '9', 42.284822, 18.84865, 2, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Wrapped in the scent of sea and sun, newly opened restaurant La Bocca, the only restaurant located on the Budva beach (Slovenska beach), offers a great variety of domestic and international dishes, all in the relaxing and welcoming atmosphere.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(313, '10017-3', 298, 24, 'MB Hotel', 7, 'Tripka Džakovića bb', 'Žabljak', '84220', '0038220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 3, 24, '8s6ybw0lmf.jpg', '', 'mbhotel', '75', '0', 43.154541, 19.12315, 24, '4, 5, 7', '<p>This award-winning hotel is located in the centre of Žabljak, just 1 km from the Savin Kuk Ski Slopes. MB Hotel features an &agrave;-la-carte restaurant and bar with a summer terrace that serves traditional cuisine, free Wi-Fi and free parking.</p>\r\n<p>All rooms at the Hotel offer heating, cable TV and a private bathroom with a shower, hairdryer and free toiletries.</p>\r\n<p>Ski storage is available on site, while ski passes can be bought at the reception. A tourist agency that organises excursions to Black Lake and rafting on Tara River can be found 150 metres away.</p>\r\n<p>Durmitor National Park also offers hiking opportunities, 1 km away. During the summer, guests can even swim in the nearby Black Lake.</p>\r\n<p>Local buses with lines to Podgorica and Nik&scaron;i? stop 150 metres away, while a train station is available in Prijepolje, 60 km from the hotel. Podgorica Airport is 100 km away.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(316, '10018-3', 298, 24, 'Hotel Mirela', 9, 'Mirošica bb', 'Sutomore', '85355', '0038220620478', '667160', '', '', 3, 17, 'vgcxxu6eys.jpg', '', 'hotelmirela', '74', '0', 42.14684, 19.037743, 17, '4, 5, 7', '<p>&nbsp;Situated 700 metres from the long and sandy Sutomore Beach, Hotel Mirela has an outdoor swimming pool and an on-site restaurant serving Montenegrin and Mediterranean specialities. The historical Nehaj Fortress boasting magnificent views is 500 metres away.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Mainly wooden furniture is featured in all accommodation units. The private bathroom comes with bath or shower.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;The centre of Sutomore with several bars and shops can be reached in a 10-minute walk. Maljevik Beach is 1 km away, and the UNESCO-protected Old Town of Bar is 5 km from the Mirela.</p>\r\n<p>Main Bus Station is 300 metres from the hotel, and the Main Train Station is at a distance of 500 metres. Podgorica Airport is 35 km away, and Mirela Hotel charges for airport shuttle service. Free private parking is available on site.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(320, '20020-3', 298, 24, 'Apartments Cungu', 9, 'Velika plaza', 'Ulcinj', '85360', '0038220620478', '667160', '', '', 3, 24, 'b3pgzpnuao.jpg', '', 'apartmentscungu', '68', '0', 41.892847, 19.296095, 24, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Apartments Cungu is located at the long beach of Ulcinj, 130 ft from the sea. It offers air conditioned apartments, free Wi-Fi, and private terraces with sea views.&nbsp;<br />Surrounded by greenery, the apartments have separate bathrooms, satellite TV and minibars.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">The restaurant serves a rich selection of national dishes. The outdoor restaurant serves grilled specialties on the grounds. Guests can start their day with a buffet breakfast every morning or choose the half board option with breakfast and dinner.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;">Apartments Cungu provides a free, secure parking lot for 15 cars.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(321, '10009-3', 345, 24, 'Dining wala', 8, 'House  1018', 'islamabad', '44000', '111111111', '667160', 'waqas@evesoft.pk', 'www.raza123.com', 2, 4, 'ib3aghxbie.jpg', '1025481651454', 'diningwala', '40', '0', 123.08451, 789.05454, 4, '4', '<p>DescriptionDescriptionDescriptionDescription</p>', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(322, '10021-3', 298, 24, 'Villa Happy', 9, 'Kava bb', 'Tivat', '85315', '0038269010208', '0038220620478', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 4, '21byvakvd5.jpg', '', 'villahappy', '68', '0', 42.444232, 18.68945, 4, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Located in a quiet area 600 metres from the pebbly beach, Villa Happy is set 1 km from the Tivat''s center and Tivat Airport. Surrounded by greenery, it offers an outdoor pool and modern-style apartments with a spa bath, a balcony and free Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p>All apartments are decorated in vivid colours and come with hardwood floors. They comprise a fully equipped kitchen with a dining and a living area. Amenities include air conditioning, an LCD satellite TV, a dishwasher and a washing machine.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to a hot tub, a terrace with barbecue facilities is also at guests&rsquo; disposal. Free private parking is possible on site.</p>\r\n<p>The nearest grocery store and a local bus stop are 300 metres away, while restaurants can be found in Tivat&rsquo;s centre. The town of Kotor is 10 km from the Villa Happy. Budva and Perast are both at a distance of 25 km.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0);
