(335, '10028-3', 298, 24, 'Hotel Perjanik', 8, 'Bralenovica', 'Danilovgrad', '81410', '0038220620478', '667160', 'milan.perovic@sunnymontenegro.com', '', 4, 15, 'b5z7ykzjbi.jpg', '', 'hotelperjanik', '75', '0', 42.56667, 19.077426, 15, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Hotel Perjanik is on the main road Niksic-Podgorica in Danilovgrad, 12 miles from Podgorica. It offers air conditioned accommodations with free Wi-Fi and satellite TV.</p>\r\n<p>The traditionally decorated restaurant serves local and international cuisine accompanied by high-quality wines.</p>\r\n<p>The Perjanik has 3 spacious terraces where you can enjoy beautiful views and fresh air of the nearby Zeta River.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
