(338, '10029-3', 298, 24, 'Apartments Kruna', 9, 'Ive lole Ribara bb, Be', 'Budva', '85315', '0038269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 2, 12, 'uujt4z7o4c.jpg', '', 'apartmentskruna', '68', '0', 42.291244, 18.869888, 12, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Just 1.2 km from Be?i?i&rsquo;s beach, Kruna offers air-conditioned accommodation with free Wi-Fi and a balcony with Adriatic Sea or city views. It has a grocery shop on site and a lush garden with a terrace and a barbecue.</p>\r\n<p>Kruna&rsquo;s rooms and apartments come with a cable TV and minibar. The apartments include a separate living room and a kitchenette. All are fitted with tiled floors and heating. Toiletries and a hairdryer are in the bathrooms.</p>\r\n<p>International buffet and &aacute; la carte dishes are served at the restaurant, which overlooks the Adriatic Sea. The 24-hour staff also provides room service. Packed lunches are available on request.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(339, '20030-3', 298, 24, 'Villa Angelina', 9, 'Kumbor bb', 'Herceg Novi', '85346', '0038269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 12, 'hepp6k1x3o.jpg', '', 'villaangelina', '68', '0', 42.436473, 18.595401, 12, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Set 70 metres from the pebbly beach, Villa Angelina is located in Kubor, 7 km from the centre of Herceg Novi. It offers accommodation with free Wi-Fi and free private parking.</p>\r\n<p>Surrounded by garden, all apartments come with a kitchenette and a private bathroom. Some feature a terrace.</p>\r\n<p>The nearest grocery store is just 30 metres from the Villa Angelina. A children`s playground is 100 metres away. Bars and restaurants can be reached within 150 metres.</p>\r\n<p>A local bus stop is 150 away. Tivat Airport is 25 km away and Podgorica Airport is at a distance of 100 km. Airport shuttle service can be arranged at a surcharge.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(340, '20004-3', 305, 47, 'Pizzeria Venom', 8, 'Svetozara Markovića 52A', 'Podgorica', '81000', '38269010208', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 0, 'enk0lriszo.jpg', '', 'pizzeriavenom', '103', '10', 42.445768, 19.254495, 0, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Quality of service, delicious food, beautiful ambience</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(341, '10031-3', 298, 24, 'Hotel Senator', 9, 'Ivana Milutinovica 51', 'Ulcinj', '85360', '0038220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 4, 12, '2lqmke0itq.jpg', '', 'hotelsenator', '75', '0', 41.926787, 19.206151, 12, '4, 5, 7', '<p>Set 1 km from the centre of Ulcinj, Hotel Senator is located 250 metres from the beach. Free Wi-Fi and a private garage are provided. The hotel offers an indoor and outdoor pool, as well as car and bike rental options.</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">All accommodation units are air-conditioned fitted with a seating area with a flat-screen TV and a DVD player. There is also a kitchenette with a dining area. Private bathroom provides a shower and hairdryer.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">The on-site bar offers a summer terrace. Massages can be enjoyed for an additional cost. There is a grocery shop 50 metres away, while a restaurant serving local and international food can be reached in 100 metres.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Airport shuttle service can be arranged for an additional cost. Podgorica Airport is 65 km away, while a Bus Station is 1 km away. The Skadar Lake can be visited 9 km from Hotel Senator.</div>\r\n<p>Set 1 km from the centre of Ulcinj, Hotel Senator is located 250 metres from the beach. Free Wi-Fi and a private garage are provided. The hotel offers an indoor and outdoor pool, as well as car and bike rental options.</p>\r\n<p>All accommodation units are air-conditioned fitted with a seating area with a flat-screen TV and a DVD player. There is also a kitchenette with a dining area. Private bathroom provides a shower and hairdryer.</p>\r\n<p>The on-site bar offers a summer terrace. Massages can be enjoyed for an additional cost. There is a grocery shop 50 metres away, while a restaurant serving local and international food can be reached in 100 metres.</p>\r\n<p>Airport shuttle service can be arranged for an additional cost. Podgorica Airport is 65 km away, while a Bus Station is 1 km away. The Skadar Lake can be visited 9 km from Hotel Senator.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1),
(342, '20032-3', 298, 24, 'Apartments Tianis', 9, 'Taba', 'Kotor', '85340', '0038220620478', '667160', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 2, 10, '1zd9l8go0q.jpg', '', 'apartmentstianis', '68', '0', 42.434626, 18.76737, 10, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 16.666667938232422px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px;">Set in a Mediterranean garden with palms, Tianis offers serviced apartments 55 yards from Kotor&rsquo;s Old Town and 55 yards from the beach. It features accommodations with private balconies and free Wi-Fi.</span></p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">At Apartments Tianis air conditioning, TV set and private bathrooms are standard. Each apartment is decorated with parquet floors and includes a lounge; most also come with a fully-equipped kitchen.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Guests can prepare their own food or enjoy a hot daily breakfast, featuring homemade bread. Breakfast is served in the outdoor patio during the warmer months or in the rooms in other periods.</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden;">Popular attractions nearby Tianis apartment-style hotel include the Romanic Saint Tryphon Cathedral. Old Kotor is UNESCO World Heritage site and provides many typical streets and panoramic views of the Adriatic Sea.</div>\r\n<p>Set in a Mediterranean garden with palms, Tianis offers serviced apartments 55 yards from Kotor&rsquo;s Old Town and 55 yards from the beach. It features accommodations with private balconies and free Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n<p>At Apartments Tianis air conditioning, TV set and private bathrooms are standard. Each apartment is decorated with parquet floors and includes a lounge; most also come with a fully-equipped kitchen.</p>\r\n<p>Guests can prepare their own food or enjoy a hot daily breakfast, featuring homemade bread. Breakfast is served in the outdoor patio during the warmer months or in the rooms in other periods.</p>\r\n<p>Popular attractions nearby Tianis apartment-style hotel include the Romanic Saint Tryphon Cathedral. Old Kotor is UNESCO World Heritage site and provides many typical streets and panoramic views of the Adriatic Sea.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(343, '10033-4', 298, 24, 'Apartments Paradiso', 9, 'Dobrota', 'Kotor', '85340', '0038269010208', '', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 0, 6, 'g40hr876mj.jpg', '', 'apartmentsparadiso', '68', '0', 42.454285, 18.765597, 6, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">Featuring a private beach just steps away, Apartments Paradiso is a seafront property in Dobrota offering air-conditioned apartments with free Wi-Fi, LCD satellite TV and splendid views of Boka Kotorska Bay. A popular beach is 200 metres away.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">The spacious apartments at the Paradiso have either a shared or a private terrace with a seating area. The kitchenette comes with a dining area, a fridge and a stove.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">The nearest grocery store and restaurant are only 40 metres from Paradiso Apartments. St. Matthew''s Church is 200 metres away. A public bus stop is 300 metres from the apartments and frequent links to Kotor are provided.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">The UNESCO-protected Old Town of Kotor is at a distance of 2.5 km, while the Main Bus Station is 3 km away. Tivat Airport is within 10 km from Paradiso Apartments. The entrance to Lov?en National Park is 40 km away.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(344, '10034-4', 298, 24, 'Apartments Mediteran', 9, 'Nikole Ljubibratica 2', 'Herceg Novi', '35360', '0038269010208', '', '', '', 3, 7, 'qrcwxgzb87.jpg', '', 'apartmentsmediteran', '68', '0', 42.46072, 18.525402, 7, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">Overlooking the Bay of Kotor and only 330 yards from the beach, Apartments Mediteran is situated in the center of Herceg Novi. It offers air-conditioned apartments with minibar and balcony.All apartments have panoramic views of the sea, private bathrooms and kitchenettes.Tennis courts, restaurants and 24-hour shops are nearby. Herceg Novi&rsquo;s 600-year-old fortress and the 9 miles beach, known as Riviera, are only a short walk from Apartments Mediteran.The Mediteran is within 30 miles of Dubrovnik and there is a local bus station within a 5-minute walk from the property.</p>', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1),
(345, '20035-4', 298, 24, 'Hotel Marshal', 7, 'Partizanski put bb', 'Niksic', '81400', '0038269010208', '', 'perovic.jasenka@gmail.com', '', 4, 0, 'likqso6dtm.jpg', '', 'hotelmarshal', '75', '0', 42.756226, 0, 0, '4, 5, 7', '<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">Featuring an &agrave;-la-carte restaurant, Hotel Marshal is located 2 km from the centre of Nik&scaron;i?. It offers air-conditioned rooms with free Wi-Fi access.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">All rooms will provide you with satellite TV and a minibar. Featuring a shower, private bathrooms also come with a hairdryer and a bathrobe. Some rooms have mountain, while some offer river views.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #003580; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 15.600000381469727px;">The nearest grocery store and a local bus stop are 200 metres away. Ostrog Monastery is at a distance of 20 km. Free on-site parking is provided.</p>', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
